  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SENIOR INTERIOR DESIGNER",
  "description": "<p>Join <strong>The Interior Place</strong>, one of Singapore’s most established and trusted interior design firms with <strong>27 years of experience</strong> and thousands of completed projects — from HDBs, condominiums to landed homes and commercial spaces.<br /></p><p>We’re expanding and looking for <strong>experienced, passionate, and results-driven Senior Interior Designers</strong> to join our creative and dynamic team.<br /></p><p><strong>What You’ll Enjoy</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Basic Salary: $4,000 – $8,000 / month + Attractive Commissions</strong></li><li><strong>Sales Incentives</strong> for high performers</li><li><strong>Guaranteed at least 80 renovation leads per year</strong></li><li>Attractive Staff Benefits & Competitive Package</li><li>Flexible Working Hours</li><li>Supportive, Collaborative & Creative Team Culture</li><li>Opportunities to work on High-Profile Projects</li><li>Ongoing Training and Professional Development</li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Meet clients to understand requirements and translate them into creative design concepts</li><li>Present design ideas confidently with proposals, mood boards, and 3D visuals</li><li>Prepare detailed quotations, drawings, and project documentation</li><li>Manage site progress to ensure timely completion and high-quality outcomes</li><li>Coordinate with suppliers, contractors, and stakeholders throughout the project</li><li>Maintain project standards, timelines, and budgets</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum 2 years of interior design experience</strong> (residential or commercial)</li><li>Strong design sensibility and communication skills</li><li>Independent, responsible, and detail-oriented</li><li>Confident in client presentations and negotiations</li><li>Familiar with Singapore’s renovation processes and authorities (bonus!)</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><p>At The Interior Place, we combine experience with creativity.<br />You’ll have the support of a <strong>trusted brand</strong>, consistent leads, and a positive team environment that values your growth and success.</p><p>✨ <strong>Apply now and let’s create amazing spaces together!</strong></p>",
